CnvrsnComment: The ESRI name used in these entries is superficial.  It was added so that a conversion to, and than from, ESRI WKT will produce the same CS-MAP name.  This was considered necessary as the CS-MAP OMAN datum definition uses the DMA multiple regression technique which is different.  Otherwise, we would just use the Fahud datum.
